## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of sources reviewed. The analysis primarily focuses on the U.S. context and may not fully capture the nuances of gender disparity in politics globally. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources means that some insights may be subject to the biases inherent in those sources.

